This R script performs robust pathway enrichment analysis for Neuroblastoma differential gene expression results.
It integrates GO, KEGG, and Reactome enrichment, producing publication-quality plots and tables for biological interpretation.

The workflow is fully automated â€” from reading DEGs to enrichment, visualization, and exporting outputs â€” and can easily be adapted to other cancer types or datasets.

